reviewText: BEST SHOW EVER! Hyper, funny, and just plain crazy! This show is so fast-paced with hilarious antics but has tear-jerking moments too. I highly recommend this show to anyone who hasn't seen it already! :) You won't regret it! This box set comes with Kodocha DVDs volume 7: "Adult Sized Secrets" and volume 8: "Sana's Duty." It also comes with a little plush Babbit! :)
Love it!! Came in brand new with volumes 7 and 8!!!
